{"tid":1465690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"818一定要叫所有人出來","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:48.000Z","uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7eafc10eee00a6bf83af3501b5db86fbb6131c","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"呢幾日軍心已經散曬，<br />\n呢四五日，葵芳亂放催淚彈，到少女爆眼、少年磨頭，克警扮鬼到太古打靶<br />\n目的就係要一次過迫癲全社會<br />\n依家大家係咁講邊個係鬼，邊個中計，邊個係乜撚物撚<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔好再分化，唔記得五年前係點樣比人打殘？</span></span><br />\n你當我和理非撚好，大台撚又好，當我發嗡風都好<br />\n八月十八號一定要來，無論克警批唔批都要來<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要複製返一百萬二百萬人個場面出來</span></span><br />\n唔係要政權收手，呢個政權係無得救<br />\n而係要提返自己，出來行係為咩<br />\n出來示威，唔只係剩係對付克警，克警只係擋箭牌<br />\n而係呢個要仆街林鄭收皮<br />\n垃圾會知道功能組別唔係大曬<br />\n要比雜種知道香港人唔好蝦<br />\n記得點解出來，唔好比仇恨spin走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n榮辱與共，同上同落<br />\n唔篤灰、唔割蓆、唔分化<br />\n要講到做到<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e23209e4b9c12c835878170fe88da91487e66eb7","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"22d2826db1fde94a6dbc7cb5fdad183ebe62cbb6","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1fcb49fd45bc851770074e5ea79bb434e34a934b","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"969df0cbfd498d8db93cedaafb36848fec39bdf5","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"93425046ae9d1f0c67564faccfff757176d79f08","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c9b18c8f6bdb68ce005d24cb6334ead33a0b431e","tid":1465690,"uid":201410,"like":0,"disl